===Noun===
'''Phoenician'''
# an inhabitant of [[Phoenicia]], a country on the eastern shores of the [[Mediterranean Sea]] around 1000 BC.
# the [[Semitic]] language spoken by the inhabitants of Phoenicia.

===Adjective===
'''Phoenician'''
# of or related to the country or [[civilisation]] of Phoenicia.

